cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on the application of deep learning methods in biomedical research, specifically in image analysis and genomics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the computational challenges of deep learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.DL (Deep Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
